card-image: img/broy.jpg
new-page: true

= Eliezer Broy

Broy is former intelligence operative and one of Dijkstra's stalwart loyalists.

As a Minister of Civil service he enforces bureaucracy's loyalty and fosters cooperation with Special Service

- cs_hiring
- cs_start_expansion
- cs_stop_expansion
- @main: Back

